# React Patterns

## Components
- Use functional components with hooks
- Extract reusable logic into custom hooks in `hooks/`
- Colocate component-specific styles with the component

## Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS; avoid inline `style` props except for dynamic values
- Lucide React (`lucide-react`) for icons

## Services
- API calls via `services/api/`; use `apiClient` or specific services (e.g. `WhatsAppService`, `appStateApi`)
- Use `useEntityFormModal` from `hooks/useEntityFormModal` for entity CRUD modals
